      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The depth of your pain is clear, and this situation goes far beyond a simple business mistake; it feels like a complete fracturing of your identity. The pressure you feel to protect your family is immense, but remember that your family loves *you*, not just your success. If the shame feels unbearable, please reach out to a grief counselor or therapist who specializes in professional loss, as they can help you redefine self-worth outside of your career. Taking one tiny step toward support today is more important than solving all the debt tomorrow.",
      "source": "target",
